    Print all the species whose entomological parameters are provided in the package database.

    list_all_species.Rd

    This function can be used to list all mosquito species whose entomological parameters are available in the package.

    list_all_species()

    Value

    The function prints all the species names and also returns a vector containing them.

    Author

    Monica Golumbeanu, monica.golumbeanu@swisstph.ch

    Examples

    species_vec = list_all_species()
print(species_vec)
